World Finance  » What is Investment? » Institutional Investment » Martin Currie Investment Management Ltd 






Martin Currie Investment Management Ltd


Martin Currie Investment Management Ltd. is a leading institutional investment management service provider based in Scotland. It offers a comprehensive range of institutional investment management services to clients located in Scotland and various other parts of the world. 










About Martin Currie Investment Management Ltd 
Martin Currie Investment Management Ltd. offers specialized institutional investment management services to a huge client base present in Scotland, the United Kingdom, the United States, and various countries of Europe and Asia. Martin Currie was incorporated in the year 1881. The company is headquartered in Edinburgh, Scotland and is governed by the Financial Services Authority (FSA).
Martin Currie Investment Management Ltd. is owned by its employees and functions in an independent mode.
Currently, it is handling portfolios worth 15.7 billion Pound Sterling or 31.3 billion U.S. dollars. The company carries out its business functions with the help of 230 employees. In Martin Currie, most of the beneficial features of both small and big investment managers are blended. For this reason, the company is nicknamed The Big Boutique.
Martin Currie Investment Management Ltd. is famous for operating in a rapid manner in order to fulfill the necessities of the increasing number of customers. Presently, the Chief Executive Officer (CEO) of Martin Currie Investment Management Ltd. is Willie Watt.
Clients of Martin Currie Investment Management 
The clients of Martin Currie Investment Management include the following:
Charitable institutions
Intermediaries
Individual investors
Foundations
Consultants and Institutional Investors 





Products and Services of Martin Currie Investment Management Ltd.
The products and services of Martin Currie Investment Management Ltd. can be categorized into the following:
Pooled institutional funds
Segregated portfolios
Investment trusts
Hedge funds
Sicav funds
Oeic funds
Business Trust
Specialist China funds
