                            Toby Hogbin
                        
Chief Operating Officer

Toby was appointed as chief operating officer of Martin Currie in March 2014, having joined the company in 2008. He was originally head of product development and was subsequently appointed director, head of marketing. Having worked in the financial-services industry for over 20 years, Toby is a highly experienced individual and has been closely involved in leading product, regulatory and business change within Martin Currie as well as leading our marketing effort into retail, institutional and hedge-fund channels globally. He is chairman of Martin Currie Fund Management Limited, the group Alternative Investment Fund Manager, and a director of MCIM and MC Inc. Toby came to us from Credit Suisse Asset Management, where he was director of products, investment solutions and marketing, and a member of the Credit Suisse Asset Management Funds (UK) Limited board.  


















